ar-03498-529x768.jpg 529w" sizes="(max-width: 137px) 100vw, 137px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="181" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-03476-290x181.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="SONY DSC" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-03476-290x181.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-03476-1024x642.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-03476-270x169.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="128" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-03049-128x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="SONY DSC" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-03049-128x200.jpg 128w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-03049-492x768.jpg 492w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-03049-270x420.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 128px) 100vw, 128px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="124" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-02544-124x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="SONY DSC" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-02544-124x200.jpg 124w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-02544-476x768.jpg 476w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-02544-270x434.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 124px) 100vw, 124px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="142" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-02333-142x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="SONY DSC" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-02333-142x200.jpg 142w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-02333-547x768.jpg 547w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Ainadamar-02333-270x378.j